{"tid":521321,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚返工時時刻刻都好似犯罪咁","createTime":"2018-01-06T12:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T04:39:11.000Z","uid":41931,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"48513d08a3c4fac37375684a7ca3575ceda552cf","tid":521321,"uid":41931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"一返去見到啲人已經圍圈，細聲講大聲笑，<br />\n直行直過好撚怪又無禮貌，打招呼又面懵，成班靜曬猶如我做錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  比啲文件同事/問人野，啲人啲態度幾撚差，老實講唔係必要都唔同你接觸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  Lunch自己食，唔小心撞到，啲所謂同事又靜曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  放工果刻都要靜靜地走，廢撚事撞到啲「同事」<br />\n<br />\n份工做左幾個月，第一日返工時啲人有扮歡迎，唔知走唔走好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ffa81ed5742ee5a01cf05255a8b33de9e02cfb","tid":521321,"uid":41931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cac23788aafba786b75e4be1be9c74b6752233","tid":521321,"uid":24045,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"你咁樣去邊間公司都係咁"},{"pid":"56dffafc1fa25533a59653b979ef95537a4d15a6","tid":521321,"uid":102689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"Same here <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209d2aa3a49fce9c03514599a81b4fc84035f3ef","tid":521321,"uid":41931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cac23788aafba786b75e4be1be9c74b6752233","tid":521321,"uid":24045,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"你咁樣去邊間公司都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"咁可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92d8be6537b99d6076c2f64fc734f5678711946","tid":521321,"uid":41931,"like":0,"dislik